nhc_headline: ...KIKO MOVING WESTWARD WITH LITTLE CHANGE IN STRENGTH...
summary: ...KIKO MOVING WESTWARD WITH LITTLE CHANGE IN STRENGTH... As of 11:00 AM HST Sun Aug 31 the center of Kiko was located near 14.4, -124.0 with movement W at 9 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1006 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 40 mph.
